<h4 id="部分分式法求解拉式反变换" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#部分分式法求解拉式反变换" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 部分分式法求解拉式反变换</h4>
<p>在控制理论中，通常有<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>F</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>s</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>B</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>s</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mi>A</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>s</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo>∑</mo><msub><mi>b</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><msup><mi>s</mi><mrow><mi>m</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>i</mi></mrow></msup></mrow><mrow><mo>∑</mo><msub><mi>a</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><msup><mi>s</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>i</mi></mrow></msup></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msubsup><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><mi>m</mi></msubsup><mfrac><msub><mi>b</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>0</mn></msub></mfrac><msup><mi>s</mi><mrow><mi>m</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>i</mi></mrow></msup></mrow><mrow><msubsup><mo>∏</mo><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><mi>n</mi></msubsup><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>s</mi><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>p</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">F(s) = \frac{B(s)}{A(s)} = \frac{\sum b_is^{m - i}}{\sum a_is^{n - i}} = \frac{\sum_{i = 0}^{m} \frac{b_i}{a_0}s^{m - i}}{\prod_{i = 0}^{n} (s + p_i)}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">F</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal">s</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.53em;vertical-align:-0.52em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mopen nulldelimiter"></span><span class="mfrac