ht:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>为方程<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>s</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">A(s) = 0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">A</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal">s</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6444em;"></span><span class="mord">0</span></span></span></span>的根的负值，称为<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>F</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>s</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">F(s)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">F</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal">s</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span>的极点，分<code v-pre>只含不同单极点</code>、<code v-pre>含共轭复数极点</code>、<code v-pre>含多重极点</code>三种情况。<br />可以通过<code v-pre>留数法</code>或者<code v-pre>通分法</code>来解决。<br /><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/40485871/1699607361444-ced19dbc-209a-43c0-be2a-4bf968383b80.png#averageHue=%23f3f3f3&amp;clientId=u52d11b25-ccc3-4&amp;from=drop&amp;height=180&amp;id=u20f3c934&amp;originHeight=888&amp;originWidth=1788&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=2&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=193823&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=ua2af6990-b7e2-49ca-b715-6dfaf83373b&amp;title=&amp;width=363" alt="截屏2023-11-10 17.09.16.png" loading="lazy"><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/40485871/1699607318520-b8de11a1-4ffc-44a8-8100-3f0c259e7748.png#averageHue=%23f0f0f0&amp;clientId=u52d11b25-ccc3-4&amp;from=drop&amp;height=189&amp;id=m0NiG&amp;originHeight=1034&amp;originWidth=1714&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=2&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=268543&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=u678235f6-73d5-4955-a742-f9143e3a798&amp;title=&amp;width=313" alt="截屏2023-11-10 17.08.32.png" loading="lazy"><br /><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/40485871/1699607382842-4bbe840b-cb96-44a7-ae5b-26c86033057a.png#averageHue=%23f5f5f5&amp;clientId=u52d11b25-ccc3-4&amp;from=drop&amp;height=231&amp;id=u976c5d5c&amp;originHeight=1100&amp;originWidth=2186&amp;originalType=binary&amp;ratio=2&amp;rotation=0&amp;showTitle=false&amp;size=340202&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;taskId=u9c294fea-6859-469a-80e5-6d3c9f3bacf&amp;title=&amp;width=460" alt="截屏2023-11-10 17.09.35.png" loading="lazy"><br>
