" style="height:0.52em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose nulldelimiter"></span></span></span></span></span>，求该系统的单位阶跃响应和单位脉冲响应。<br />解：由题可知单位反馈系统的闭环传递函数为<br /><span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>G</mi><mi>k</mi></msub><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>s</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>G</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>s</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mi>G</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>s</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mfrac><mn>4</mn><mrow><mi>s</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>s</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>5</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>4</mn><mrow><mi>s</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>s</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>5</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mfrac></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>4</mn><mrow><msup><mi>s</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>5</mn><mi>s</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>4</mn><mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>s</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>s</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">G_{k}(s) = \frac{G(s)}{1+G(s)} = \frac{\frac{4}{s(s+5)}}{1+\frac{4}{s(s+5)}}=\frac{4}{s^{2}+5s+4}=\frac{4}{(s+1)(s+4)}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal">G</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3361em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span cl